  # ABILITIES
  _basicAttack:
    abilityId: mealea_ribbon_strike
    abilityName: Silk Ribbon Dance
    description: Graceful ribbon attacks that flow from one enemy to the next.
    damage: 15
    cooldown: 0
    staminaCost: 4
    range: 3
    type: Melee
    element: Light

  _specialAbility:
    abilityId: mealea_healing_dance
    abilityName: Dance of Restoration
    description: |
      Mealea performs a sacred dance that heals all allies and removes negative 
      status effects. The more injured the ally, the more they're healed.
    damage: 0
    cooldown: 14
    staminaCost: 40
    range: 10
    type: Heal
    element: Light
    statusEffects:
      - heal_percentage_30
      - cleanse_debuffs

  _ultimateAbility:
    abilityId: mealea_divine_performance
      abilityName: Divine Apsara Performance
    description: |
      Mealea ascends and performs the legendary Dance of Creation. Time seems 
      to slow as lotus petals rain down. All allies are fully healed and 
      empowered, while enemies are mesmerized, unable to attack.
    damage: 0
    cooldown: 60
    staminaCost: 90
    range: 20
    type: Buff
    element: Light
    statusEffects:
      - full_heal_allies
      - attack_boost_50
      - enemy_mesmerize_4s

  _passiveAbility:
    abilityId: mealea_grace
    abilityName: Celestial Grace
    description: |
      Mealea's divine nature means she floats slightly above ground and cannot 
      be slowed. Her mere presence gradually heals nearby allies.
    damage: 0
    cooldown: 0
    staminaCost: 0
    range: 8
    type: Buff
    element: Light

  _comboMoves:
    - abilityId: mealea_petal_storm
      abilityName: Lotus Petal Storm
      description: Razor-sharp flower petals spin around Mealea, damaging nearby enemies.
      damage: 35
      cooldown: 0
      staminaCost: 18
      type: AoE
      
    - abilityId: mealea_blessing
      abilityName: Individual Blessing
      description: Touch an ally to grant them temporary invincibility.
      damage: 0
      cooldown: 20
      staminaCost: 35
      type: Buff

  # PERSONALITY
  _personality:
    bravery: 65
    kindness: 100
    wisdom: 70
    humor: 55
    loyalty: 85
    curiosity: 100

  _likes:
    - Watching mortals live their lives
    - New experiences (everything is new!)
    - Dancing (of course)
    - Flowers and gardens
    - Kavi's jokes (she doesn't understand them but laughs anyway)

  _dislikes:
    - The cold detachment of some celestials
    - Seeing others in pain
    - Not understanding mortal customs
    - Being treated as divine and untouchable
    - Spicy food (too overwhelming!)

  _favoriteFood: Sweet rice with mango (her first mortal food - life-changing!)
  _hobby: Learning mortal customs and trying new experiences
  _fear: That she'll have to return to heaven and leave her friends behind
  _dream: To understand what it truly means to be "alive"

  # VOICE LINES
  _voiceLines:
    lines:
      - type: Greeting
        text: "Oh! Hello, dear friend! Is this how mortals greet? *waves enthusiastically*"
      - type: Greeting
        text: "Every meeting is a blessing. The gods say so!"
      - type: Selection
        text: "You chose me? I'm... honored! Is 'honored' the right word?"
      - type: Selection
        text: "Let us dance through this challenge together!"
      - type: BattleStart
        text: "I do not wish to fight, but I will protect those I love!"
      - type: BattleStart
        text: "My dance... can be a weapon too."
      - type: Attack
        text: "With grace!"
      - type: Attack
        text: "Forgive me!"
      - type: SpecialAttack
        text: "Let my dance heal your wounds!"
      - type: Ultimate
        text: "Witness the Dance of Creation! DIVINE PERFORMANCE!"
      - type: Hurt
        text: "Ah! So this is... pain?"
      - type: LowHealth
        text: "Is this what mortals call... fear?"
      - type: Victory
        text: "We prevailed! I feel... happiness? Yes, happiness!"
      - type: Victory
        text: "The dance is complete. *bows gracefully*"
      - type: Defeat
        text: "I have... failed? This feeling is unpleasant..."
      - type: LevelUp
        text: "I grow stronger! The gods would never believe this!"
      - type: Idle
        text: "*practices dance moves* One and two and three and..."
      - type: Idle
        text: "That cloud looks like Kavi! ...Every cloud looks like Kavi to me now."
      - type: Funny
        text: "Kavi told me a 'knock knock joke.' Who is knocking? Should I answer?"
      - type: Funny
        text: "I tried 'sleeping' last night. Mortals do this EVERY day?! Remarkable!"

  # RELATIONSHIPS
  _relationships:
    - characterId: kavi_monkey
      characterName: Kavi
      type: Friend
      affinity: 70
      relationshipDescription: |
        Mealea finds Kavi utterly fascinating. His chaos is so... alive! She 
        doesn't understand his jokes but laughs because his joy is contagious.
        She's oblivious to his crush on her.
      specialDialogue:
        - "Kavi makes strange sounds with his mouth. 'Jokes,' he calls them. Delightful!"
        - "Why does he trip whenever I look at him? Is he unwell?"

    - characterId: champa_elephant
      characterName: Champa
      type: Friend
      affinity: 85
      relationshipDescription: |
        Champa is like a mother figure to Mealea, teaching her about the mortal 
        world. They share a love of gentleness and protecting others.
      specialDialogue:
        - "Champa explains mortal things without making me feel foolish."
        - "She has such a beautiful heart. Even the gods would admire her."

    - characterId: singha_lion
      characterName: Singha
      type: Friend
      affinity: 75
      relationshipDescription: |
        Singha's noble nature reminds Mealea of the divine guardians in heaven. 
        She respects his sense of duty and often dances to soothe his serious mood.
      specialDialogue:
        - "Singha is so... serious. I shall teach him to smile more!"
        - "His roar is like celestial music. Powerful and beautiful."

  # BACKSTORY
  _birthplace: Celestial Palace Above the Clouds
  _occupation: Celestial Dancer / Guardian of Light
  _familyBackground: |
    Apsaras don't have families in the mortal sense. Mealea was "created" rather 
    than born. But she considers her fellow Apsaras as sisters, even if they 
    find her too emotional.
  _backstory: |
    See full biography above.
  _keyMemories:
    - "The first time I tasted food. Sweet rice with mango. I cried. I'd never cried before."
    - "Dancing for the gods and feeling... nothing. Then watching a mortal wedding and feeling... everything."
    - "Being chosen for this mission and feeling terrified and thrilled."
    - "Kavi making me laugh until my stomach hurt. I didn't know stomachs could do that!"

